donation_message: "I gave to this project because I have experienced the magic of this school and the life-long impact it has on the fortunate students there."
"I helped because I'm a strong believer in Literature & Writing education."
"I gave to this project because we want Mrs. P. to have a fully equipt classroom. "
"I gave to this project because my daughter had the pleasure of being in Ms. A's class last year and we know what a great teacher she is!"

"I gave because I want Lily, Sarah and Grace to shine on.  This fund is incredible and lets the girls live on within these classrooms.  I am a lamp designer and intend to give 20 percent of my sales to this fund.  www.lightingbylucia.com"
"I donated because I want to support kids in Florida."
"Matching donation by the DonorsChoose.org Board of Directors. Best of luck with this project!"
"I gave to this project because I want the class to have the best materials available so that they can have fun while learning!!"

"I gave because I want kids to discover the joy of reading. It is an important part of my own life and I hope my small donation will do some good in order to make books an important part of your lives too."
